headline: The Home Depot and The Home Depot Foundation commit $1 million to Hurricane Melissa relief efforts
summary: The Home Depot and The Home Depot Foundation are committing $1 million in product donations, nonprofit grants and other support to provide immediate relief and long-term recovery support to Jamaica and other Caribbean communities devastated by Hurricane Melissa, one of the strongest storms in the region's history.
